            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size:36px;margin:0 0 6px">Pre‑exec → Decide → Runtime → Identity → Prove</h2>
                <ul style="margin:10px 0 0 18px;color:#9ba3b7;line-height:1.8">
                    <li><strong>Pre‑execution (MCP Gateway):</strong> validate plan & schema pins; block injection/overreach before models run.</li>
